Package com.emmes.aps Description

APS application main package



The aps pakcage contains all the activities of the android application together with some other helping classes.
The main application starts from APSApplication file which also contains some provisions like when to show the which screen to the user. This file also contains the MokiManage mobility settings.
SplashScreen is implemented here for keeping the user waiting displaying some eye catching animation or some important information while the others things of the app are loading to the system.
MainActivity is the entry point to the application. While the application is loading for the homepage, MainActivity decides about the login and new entry MainActivity#settingsExist.
